item.title: Google Code Jam 2018
item.description: Codejam is using a different system and rules than before. I’m not sure if I want to participate in the contest. I know how to solve problem A , but I can’t find a vital bit of info about the new rules like the CPU of the servers where the codes are supposed to run. However, this suspiciously sound like one of those badly made ACM contests. I no longer have so much free time as before.
